trends: There has been one other sighting in Deerfield
There were no other sightings in Deerfield on or around October 31st 2008
divs: Sighting DetailsOut on Halloween night not long after dusk and happened to see a slow sparkly green fireball cut across maybe 10-15% of the skyline. It was primarily green but sparkled and p articulated in all colors of the spectrum. The decent lasted about 8-10sec and had residual visibility for another 5 seconds or so. I have never seen a decent as bright or colorful as this.
